PrecisApproval to enter into a SUPPLEMENTARY AGREEMENT with QUEBEC in order to amend Part VII of the AGREEMENT with respect to the ADMINISTRATION BY QUEBEC OF PART IX of the EXCISE TAX ACT relating to the GOODS AND SERVICES TAX so that the actual ratio used to calculate the ceiling on the compensation payable to Quebec shall be that of the previous fiscal year.
